      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/22/2/6/12",
      "text": [
        ": سمعت جابر بن سمرة يقول: سمعت رسول الله قال: يقوم بعده - أو من بعده - اثنا عشر أميراً. ثم تكلم بكلمة لم أفهمها فسألت القوم ما قال؟ فقالوا: قال: كلهم من قريش."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(12) Khalaf bin al-Waleed al-Lu’lu’iy narrated from Sammak that Jabir bin Samra had said: “I heard the Prophet (S) saying that there would be twelve emirs after him. Then he said something that I could not understand. I asked some people what he had said. They told me that he had said: “All of them are from Quraysh.”"
        ]
      }
    },
